This code bundle should be used in conjuntion with the "Embedded Linux Projects
Using Yocto Project Cookbook" 2nd edition published by Packt Publising.

The directories are named with the chapter and recipe number they belong to:

CH_N

where,

CH is the chapter number
N is the recipe number

Inside the chapter directories there is:

* Source code
* Metadata inside the meta-bsp-custom and meta-custom directories
* Command line and configuration lines inside the 'commands.README' file
* local.conf and bblayers.conf files when applicable inside the conf/ directory

Please forward erratas to http://www.packtpub.com/submit-errata
